OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1775837470
OL,3,CMoon mission or massive hoax? Why
OL,4,CArtemis II reignited space conspiracy
OL,5,Ctheories
OL,7,FBy ITV News Producer Hannah Ward-
OL,8,FGlenton
OL,10,FOver the last 10 days, the Artemis II
OL,11,Fmission has captured the world's
OL,12,Fattention.
OL,14,FPeople have closely followed the
OL,15,Fmission around the moon, marvelling at
OL,16,Fthe footage captured by the team and
OL,17,Fshared by Nasa, widely regarded as the
OL,18,Fworld's leading space exploration
OL,19,Forganisation.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1775837470
OL,3,CMoon mission or massive hoax? Why
OL,4,CArtemis II reignited space conspiracy
OL,5,Ctheories
OL,7,FBut not all of the responses have been
OL,8,Fpositive.
OL,10,FPhotos, videos, and news coverage of
OL,11,Fthe space mission have received
OL,12,Fhundreds, if not thousands, of
OL,13,Fskeptical comments online suggesting
OL,14,Fthe content is fake. In more extreme
OL,15,Fcases, people have even claimed the
OL,16,Fmission itself is staged.
OL,18,FHere, ITV News looks at why Artemis II
OL,19,Fhas triggered a flurry of conspiracy
OL,20,Ftheories.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1775837470
OL,3,CMoon mission or massive hoax? Why
OL,4,CArtemis II reignited space conspiracy
OL,5,Ctheories
OL,7,FWhat are the conspiracy theories
OL,8,Faround Artemis II?
OL,10,FOne of the most common conspiracy
OL,11,Ftheories around the Artemis II mission
OL,12,Fis that it did not happen at all, and
OL,13,Fmay have been staged using green
OL,14,Fscreens.
OL,16,FOne video, which has been viewed over
OL,17,Fone million times, shows the
OL,18,Fastronauts suspended by wires in front
OL,19,Fof a prop space capsule, as if a
OL,20,Fstudio is trying to recreate the look
OL,21,Fof weightlessness in space.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1775837470
OL,3,CMoon mission or massive hoax? Why
OL,4,CArtemis II reignited space conspiracy
OL,5,Ctheories
OL,7,FThe footage is AI-generated, created
OL,8,Fusing Google AI, according to the
OL,9,Fcompany's SynthID watermark check tool.
OL,11,FOther conspiracy theories revolve
OL,12,Faround how photographs Nasa shared of
OL,13,Fthe far side of the moon. They claim
OL,14,Fthe images must be fake because there
OL,15,Fis light in the photos.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1775837470
OL,3,CMoon mission or massive hoax? Why
OL,4,CArtemis II reignited space conspiracy
OL,5,Ctheories
OL,7,FBut Nasa explained the reason behind
OL,8,Fthe light in a statement on April 3,
OL,9,Fsaying: "During the six-hour lunar
OL,10,Fscience observation period, the Sun,
OL,11,FMoon, and the Orion spacecraft will be
OL,12,Faligned such that the crew will see
OL,13,Fabout 20% of the Moon's far side, the
OL,14,Fhemisphere not visible from Earth, lit
OL,15,Fby the Sun".
OL,17,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,18,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,19,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,20,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1775837470
OL,3,CMoon mission or massive hoax? Why
OL,4,CArtemis II reignited space conspiracy
OL,5,Ctheories
OL,7,FThere were also questions over details
OL,8,Fin some TV coverage of in-space press
OL,9,Fconferences, which appeared to show a
OL,10,Frandom logo projected onto a plush toy
OL,11,Fin the capsule.
OL,13,FThis was widely quashed as a technical
OL,14,Ferror by the TV station rather than
OL,15,Fproof of the mission being faked.
OL,17,FConspiracy theories around Artemis II
OL,18,Fhave been perpetuated and elevated by
OL,19,Fwell-known people.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1775837470
OL,3,CMoon mission or massive hoax? Why
OL,4,CArtemis II reignited space conspiracy
OL,5,Ctheories
OL,7,FFormer British MP Andrew Bridgen, for
OL,8,Fexample, shared two photos with his
OL,9,F361,000 followers, claiming one was
OL,10,Ffrom the Apollo 8 mission in 1968 and
OL,11,Fone was Artemis II.
OL,13,F"It's a remarkable coincidence that
OL,14,Fthe Earth was exactly the same
OL,15,Forientation to the moon with exactly
OL,16,Fthe same cloud coverage when these two
OL,17,Fpictures were taken 68 years apart. Am
OL,18,FI now a coincidence theorist ?" he
OL,19,Fwrote on X.
OL,26,@zD@_O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1775837470
OL,3,CMoon mission or massive hoax? Why
OL,4,CArtemis II reignited space conspiracy
OL,5,Ctheories
OL,7,FSocial media users quickly noted that
OL,8,Fthe second image was not from the
OL,9,FArtemis II mission at all.
OL,11,FWhere do space conspiracy theories
OL,12,Fcome from?
OL,14,FDoubts around the Artemis II mission
OL,15,Fare by no means the first conspiracy
OL,16,Ftheories around space travel.
OL,18,FHoax rumours around the moon landings
OL,19,Fin 1969 weren't uncommon at the time,
OL,20,Fand they have continued to circulate
OL,21,Fin the decades since then.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1775837470
OL,3,CMoon mission or massive hoax? Why
OL,4,CArtemis II reignited space conspiracy
OL,5,Ctheories
OL,7,FThere were, and still are, beliefs
OL,8,Fthat the Apollo moon landings were a
OL,9,FHollywood production, designed to
OL,10,Fsuggest the US had won the Space Race.
OL,12,FThere have been doubts cast over
OL,13,Fshadows in the photos, whether humans
OL,14,Fcould survive Earth's radiation field,
OL,15,Fa lack of stars in photos, and why
OL,16,Fhumans haven't yet returned to the
OL,17,Fmoon - all of which have been
OL,18,Frigorously debunked multiple times by
OL,19,Fscientists.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30510
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1775837470
OL,3,CMoon mission or massive hoax? Why
OL,4,CArtemis II reignited space conspiracy
OL,5,Ctheories
OL,7,FWhy has Artemis II triggered
OL,8,Fconspiracy theories?
OL,10,FWhile there has been a wave of Artemis
OL,11,FII disinformation circulating in the
OL,12,Flast 10 days, all major events tend to
OL,13,Fgenerate conspiracy theories,
OL,14,Faccording to Professor Peter Knight,
OL,15,Fwho researches conspiracy theories at
OL,16,Fthe University of Manchester.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30511
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1775837470
OL,3,CMoon mission or massive hoax? Why
OL,4,CArtemis II reignited space conspiracy
OL,5,Ctheories
OL,7,F"It's no surprise that the first
OL,8,Fmanned orbit of the moon for half a
OL,9,Fcentury has led to a resurgence of
OL,10,Fmoon landing conspiracy theories. None
OL,11,Fof this is new, but what has changed
OL,12,Fis that conspiracy theories are now
OL,13,Ffar more visible to ordinary people,"
OL,14,Fhe said.
OL,16,FWith people spending hours online, the
OL,17,Flevel of exposure to material
OL,18,Fcirculating on social media is
OL,19,Finevitably greater.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30512
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1775837470
OL,3,CMoon mission or massive hoax? Why
OL,4,CArtemis II reignited space conspiracy
OL,5,Ctheories
OL,7,FThe context around the Artemis II
OL,8,Fconspiracy theories is also very
OL,9,Fsimilar to the narrative around the
OL,10,Ffirst moon landing being a hoax,
OL,11,Faccording to Dr Ilya Yablokov,
OL,12,FLecturer in Digital Journalism and
OL,13,FDisinformation and co-lead of the
OL,14,FDisinformation Research Cluster at the
OL,15,FUniversity of Sheffield.
OL,17,FMr Yablokov said these theories are
OL,18,Foften rooted in a broader distrust of
OL,19,Fpowerful institutions and their
OL,20,Fmotives.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30513
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1775837470
OL,3,CMoon mission or massive hoax? Why
OL,4,CArtemis II reignited space conspiracy
OL,5,Ctheories
OL,7,FThey also include the idea that
OL,8,Fnations - particularly the United
OL,9,FStates and China - are attempting to
OL,10,F"weaponise space", reinforcing the
OL,11,Fsuspicion that these missions serve
OL,12,Fhidden agendas rather than the
OL,13,Fadvancement of humanity.
OL,15,F"In that sense, what we saw 50 years
OL,16,Fago with the Apollo moon landing, we
OL,17,Fsee today. Because in a sense these
OL,18,Fare very similar triggers and factors
OL,19,Fthat help these conspiracy theories to
OL,20,Fproliferate," he added.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30514
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1775837470
OL,3,CMoon mission or massive hoax? Why
OL,4,CArtemis II reignited space conspiracy
OL,5,Ctheories
OL,7,FDistrust of experts, institutions, and
OL,8,Fthe government has been increasing
OL,9,Fsince the 1970s, according to
OL,10,FProfessor Knight, and is fundamental
OL,11,Fto the dissemination of conspiracy
OL,12,Ftheories.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30515
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1775837470
OL,3,CMoon mission or massive hoax? Why
OL,4,CArtemis II reignited space conspiracy
OL,5,Ctheories
OL,7,F"The original moon landing conspiracy
OL,8,Ftheories were in part a response to a
OL,9,Floss of trust in the American
OL,10,Fgovernment in the wake of the
OL,11,Fpolitical assassinations of the 1960s,
OL,12,Fthe Vietnam War, and Watergate. Now,
OL,13,Fthe distrust of experts and
OL,14,Finstitutions is even more widespread,"
OL,15,Fhe told ITV News.
OL,17,F"They can spring from genuine feelings
OL,18,Fof resentment or distrust that can't
OL,19,Fsimply be dismissed as paranoid
OL,20,Fdelusions," he added.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30516
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1775837470
OL,3,CMoon mission or massive hoax? Why
OL,4,CArtemis II reignited space conspiracy
OL,5,Ctheories
OL,7,FThere are also people "cynically
OL,8,Fjumping on the bandwagon to help
OL,9,Fpromote their social media feed" and
OL,10,Fusing conspiracy theories to do that,
OL,11,Fhe added.
OL,13,FHas AI changed how conspiracy theories
OL,14,Fwork?
OL,16,FWhile artificial intelligence has been
OL,17,Fused to create fake content around the
OL,18,FArtemis II mission, it has also made
OL,19,Fpeople more distrustful of genuine
OL,20,Ffootage.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G16/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30517
SC,0017
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1775837470
OL,3,CMoon mission or massive hoax? Why
OL,4,CArtemis II reignited space conspiracy
OL,5,Ctheories
OL,7,F"This time round, there's often the
OL,8,Fsuggestion that it's all AI-
OL,9,Fgenerated... It's not that people
OL,10,Fbelieve in crazy things that aren't
OL,11,Ftrue; instead, they refuse to believe
OL,12,Fin things that are actually real,
OL,13,Finsisting instead that it's all fake
OL,14,Fnews or AI-generated," Professor
OL,15,FKnight said.
OL,17,FWhat are the consequences?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G17/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30518
SC,0018
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1775837470
OL,3,CMoon mission or massive hoax? Why
OL,4,CArtemis II reignited space conspiracy
OL,5,Ctheories
OL,7,FThe spread of conspiracy theories
OL,8,Fdoesn't necessarily have huge
OL,9,Fconsequences for an individual, Dr
OL,10,FYablokov said, but there can be huge
OL,11,Fknock-on effects at an institutional
OL,12,Flevel.
OL,14,FThis can be especially problematic if
OL,15,Fa person who, for example, didn't
OL,16,Fbelieve that humans have landed on the
OL,17,Fmoon is put in a position of power.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G18/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30519
SC,0019
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1775837470
OL,3,CMoon mission or massive hoax? Why
OL,4,CArtemis II reignited space conspiracy
OL,5,Ctheories
OL,7,F"So imagine this person says, oh,
OL,8,Flook, I don't think it's important. I
OL,9,Fdon't think we should waste our money
OL,10,Fon that. That would put missions under
OL,11,Fthreat.
OL,13,F"If those beliefs are weaponised or
OL,14,Fendorsed by influential people, then
OL,15,Fthat would be a problem. It would
OL,16,Fbecome a problem for societies, for
OL,17,Four race to explore the universe," he
OL,18,Fadded.
OL,20,FShould, and can, conspiracy theories
OL,21,Fbe stopped?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G19/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30520
SC,0020
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1775837470
OL,3,CMoon mission or massive hoax? Why
OL,4,CArtemis II reignited space conspiracy
OL,5,Ctheories
OL,7,FConspiracy theories have always been
OL,8,Faround, and "will stay around", Dr
OL,9,FYablokov said.
OL,11,FSocial media just allows for any
OL,12,Fperson's beliefs to be amplified, and
OL,13,Fit does not discriminate based on
OL,14,Fwhether or not the person posting
OL,15,Fknows anything about the subject
OL,16,Fmatter.
OL,18,F"It's a long-term game. We simply need
OL,19,Fto do whatever we can ... We need to
OL,20,Fmake sure that people understand the
OL,21,Fvalue of (space programmes)."
OL,26,@}D@Jpm}D@[pn
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G20/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30521
SC,0021
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1775837470
OL,3,CMoon mission or massive hoax? Why
OL,4,CArtemis II reignited space conspiracy
OL,5,Ctheories
OL,7,FProfessor Knight added that a sense of
OL,8,Ftrust and democratic buy-in for
OL,9,Fscience and scientific institutions
OL,10,Fwould be one of the only ways to fully
OL,11,Fdisprove conspiracy theories.
OL,13,FAnd that, he said, "is long, slow,
OL,14,Fhard work".
OL,16,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,17,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,18,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,19,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,20,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
